Title: Show employee roles with overridden methods
Description: Create a class Employee with method role() printing â€œGeneral Employeeâ€. Create child classes Manager, Clerk, Tester, each overriding role() to print their specific roles. Call role() on each object to show how overriding helps in specialization.
